    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-051__align-001">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-051</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 51.1 - 老子 51.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 51.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>道生之，德畜之，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>All things are produced by the Dao, and nourished by its outflowing operation.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-051__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-051</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">4</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 51.3 - 老子 51.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 51.2 - 老子 51.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>物形之，勢成之。是以萬物莫不尊道而貴德。道之尊，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>They receive their forms according to the nature of each, and are completed according to the circumstances of their condition. Therefore all things without exception honour the Dao, and exalt its outflowing operation.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-051__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-051</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 51.7 - 老子 51.8</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 51.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>德之貴，夫莫之命而常自然。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>This honouring of the Dao and exalting of its operation is not the result of any ordination, but always a spontaneous tribute.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-051__align-004">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-051</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">4</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 51.9 - 老子 51.12</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 51.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>故道生之，德畜之。長之育之，亭之毒之，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Thus it is that the Dao produces (all things), nourishes them, brings them to their full growth, nurses them, completes them, matures them, maintains them, and overspreads them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-051__align-005">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-051</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 51.13</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 51.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>蓋之覆之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>It produces them and makes no claim to the possession of them;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-051__align-006">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-051</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 51.14 - 老子 51.15</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 51.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>生而不有，為而不恃，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>it carries them through their processes and does not vaunt its ability in doing so;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-051__align-007">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-051</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 51.16 - 老子 51.17</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 51.8 - 老子 51.9</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>長而不宰。是謂玄德。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>it brings them to maturity and exercises no control over them; - this is called its mysterious operation.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
